<P>Is this Blood &s;uch quickning Blood? Then, <HI>Lord, I am a&s;hamed, that my heart hath been, and is &s;o dull; that I have brought &s;uch a dead <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="2 letters">art to behold my dying Lord: But if it be a quickning B<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">ood, then, O that I might feel and <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">ind it to be &s;o.</HI></P>
