<P>Is this indeed &s;uch mortifying Blood? Oh <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">hen, <HI>what did I do when I did neglect to bring <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">y <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">usts unto it, but to con&s;ult how they may
