</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>M.</SPEAKER>
<P><HI>Why is Knowledge nece&s;sary?</HI></P>
</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>C.</SPEAKER>
<P>Becau&s;e without knowledge the heart cannot be good, <HI>Prov</HI> 19.2 Nor can a man el&s;e examine him&s;elf, or di&s;cern the Lords Body.</P>
</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>M</SPEAKER>
<P><HI>What knowledge is nece&s;sary?</HI></P>
</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>C.</SPEAKER>
