</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>M.</SPEAKER>
<P><HI>But if a man cannot &s;ay, he loves God, and &s;ay, he hath faith, but yet find he hunger after Christ and thirsteth for him, may he comes to the Lords Table?</HI></P>
