</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>M.</SPEAKER>
<P><HI>If upon &s;erious &s;earch you find the&s;e Graces wrought in your heart; is it nece&s;sary you &s;hould &s;pend &s;ome time in &s;olemn prayer before you go?</HI></P>
